inclusion.criterion: Normal serum testosterone, LH and FSH
inclusion.label: met

inclusion.criterion: Agrees not to donate blood or participate in another research study during the study
inclusion.label: met

inclusion.criterion: In general good health based on normal screening evaluation (consisting of a medical history, physical exam, normal sperm count, normal serum chemistry and hematology)
inclusion.label: met

inclusion.criterion: Must be willing to use a reliable form of contraception during the study
inclusion.label: met

exclusion.criterion: Oligospermia (sperm count < 15 million/mL after 48 hours of abstinence) and/or abnormal motility or morphology.
exclusion.label: not_met

exclusion.criterion: Participation in a long-term male contraceptive study within the past three months
exclusion.label: unknown
